OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773558304
OL,3,CA warning from Wall Street: Global
OL,4,Cfuel shortage may be days away
OL,6,FA prominent Wall Street bank has
OL,7,Fwarned the continued closure of the
OL,8,FStrait of Hormuz will have a
OL,9,Fsignificant economic impact across
OL,10,Fmultiple sectors, as ITV News
OL,11,FEconomics Editor Joel Hills reports
OL,13,FUS President Donald Trump has publicly
OL,14,Fdismissed concerns about rising fuel
OL,15,Fprices since the conflict began.
OL,17,FHigher oil prices, he said, are "a
OL,18,Fvery small price" to pay for the
OL,19,Fincreased security that Operation Epic
OL,20,FFury will deliver for ordinary
OL,21,FAmericans.
OL,26,@yD@aOUzD@QO]
