OL,3,CA warning from Wall Street: Global
OL,4,Cfuel shortage may be days away
OL,6,FBut tonight a prominent Wall Street
OL,7,Fbank has warned that the economic
OL,8,Fimpact of the closure of the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz - a vital shipping lane for oil
OL,10,Fand gas - could intensify dramatically
OL,11,Fin the coming days as shortages emerge.
OL,13,FIn a research note published on Friday
OL,14,Fevening, Natasha Kaneva, head of
OL,15,Fcommodities research at JPMorgan
OL,16,FChase, wrote: "By the end of next
OL,17,Fweek, we expect crude supply cuts to
OL,18,Fapproach 12 million barrels per day,
OL,19,Fmaking the deficit highly visible
OL,20,Facross physical markets."
OL,26,@xD@OOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
