OL,3,CA warning from Wall Street: Global
OL,4,Cfuel shortage may be days away
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThat is an enormous amount of oil to
OL,12,Fdisappear. For context, the world
OL,13,Fnormally consumes around 100 million
OL,14,Fbarrels a day.
OL,16,FThe JPMorgan note adds: "The market is
OL,17,Ffacing an acute shortage of products -
OL,18,Fdiesel, jet fuel, LPG and naphtha -
OL,19,Fthat cannot be consumed simply because
OL,20,Fthey are not available."
OL,26,@xD@YOU|D@XO]
