OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773558304
OL,3,CA warning from Wall Street: Global
OL,4,Cfuel shortage may be days away
OL,6,FIn plain English: the problem isn't
OL,7,Fjust oil prices. The world is running
OL,8,Fshort of the fuels that power cars,
OL,9,Florries, aircraft, factories and farms.
OL,11,FThe first visible effects of the shock
OL,12,Fare already appearing in Asian
OL,13,Fcountries that depend heavily on
OL,14,Fenergy exports from the Gulf.
OL,16,FIndia, Bangladesh, Sri Lanka and
OL,17,FVietnam are already rationing fuel or
OL,18,Fpreparing emergency measures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
