PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773558304
OL,3,CA warning from Wall Street: Global
OL,4,Cfuel shortage may be days away
OL,6,FAirlines in Australia have raised
OL,7,Fairfares, while Air New Zealand has
OL,8,Fbegun cancelling flights.
OL,10,F"We have never been in this situation
OL,11,Fbefore," Neil Atkinson, the former
OL,12,Fhead of oil markets at the
OL,13,FInternational Energy Agency, told ITV
OL,14,FNews
OL,16,FNeil Atkinson, the former head of oil
OL,17,Fmarkets at the International Energy
OL,18,FAgency (IEA), describes the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz as the "single most important
OL,20,Fchoke point in global shipping" - even
OL,21,Fmore critical than the Suez Canal.
OL,26,@rD@AOU{D@OOU|D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
