PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773558304
OL,3,CA warning from Wall Street: Global
OL,4,Cfuel shortage may be days away
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News, he
OL,7,Fexplained that the IEA used to run war-
OL,8,Fgame scenarios simulating major
OL,9,Fdisruptions to oil supply.
OL,11,FBut they never seriously considered
OL,12,Fthe Strait of Hormuz closing.
OL,14,FIt was considered unthinkable because
OL,15,Fof the shortages it would create.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
