PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773558304
OL,3,CA warning from Wall Street: Global
OL,4,Cfuel shortage may be days away
OL,6,F"We have never been in this situation
OL,7,Fbefore. We've had interruptions to oil
OL,8,Fand gas supply in the past - the
OL,9,FIranian revolution in 1979, the first
OL,10,FGulf War in 1990, the invasion of Iraq
OL,11,Fin 2003, Russia's invasion of Ukraine
OL,12,Ffour years ago," Atkinson said.
OL,14,F"Not one of them comes close to what
OL,15,Fis actually happening today in the
OL,16,FStrait of Hormuz."
OL,18,FPresident Trump is right when he
OL,19,Fargues that the United States is less
OL,20,Fexposed to the energy shock because it
OL,21,Fis the world's largest producer of oil.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@RO]
